Dramatician
[[Image:Sexy_times.jpg|thumb|right|typical dramatician's weekend.]]
A '''Dramatician''' is one who is versed in compiling and cataloging internet drama. All power users and [[early adopter]]s of [[ED]], [[ljdrama]] and [[frienditto]] are considered dramaticians.

Dramaticians at [[ED]] now have their very own [[LiveJournal]] community in which to discuss the scientific method when dealing with [[drama]] and other aspects of their skill. The [http://www.livejournal.com/userinfo.bml?user=dramaticians Dramaticians] (there hasnt been a post there since june of 07) community has plenty of resources for both the well seasoned professional and the weekend hobbyist.




